i am unable to reproduce this with Adobe Reader 9.5.0, Preview 5.0.3;

there is also no problem with loading PDFs using the itext RUPS utility (com.itextpdf.rups.Rups);

however, i can confirm the problem is still present with Adobe Reader 10.1.2;

i'm moving this to resolved+wontfix, and recommend that someone report a bug to Adobe; if someone wishes to investigate this in FOP and can identify an FOP issue (and fix) that is triggering this Adobe bug, then it can be reopened to perform the fix;

i did the above tests on Mac OS X 10.6.8
